Package engine

Class Summary
GameEngine GameEngine to run Simulations and tournaments using the Brain and World objects specified.
GameEngineTest  
GameStats Class to hold scores generated by the run of a simulation.
Random Random to generate pseudorandom numbers between 0 (inclusive) and the value given (exclusive)
Simulation Simulation to, when given a World, and two Brain objects, allow the Ants in the World to move, according to their Brains, and to record the result after a number of steps have passed.
SoundPlayer A class which allows the playing of four different sound effects.
